{"vo",file="fem_kzd_000191",ch="kzd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"雫","葛"},
"「水菜さんが……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00205",
linknext="block_00207",
},
block_00207={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「そう、身の危険を感じたら絶対逃げると約束してほしいって、な」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00206",
linknext="block_00208",
